uring a standalone bathtub, rain forest shower.','Fabulous Lagoon Oasis','','publish','closed','closed','','fabulous-lagoon-oasis','','','2016-10-15 02:27:42','2016-10-14 20:42:42','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/?post_type=room&#038;p=466',0,'room','',0),(467,1,'2016-10-15 02:27:17','2016-10-14 20:42:17','','w-maldives-lagoon-oasis-tmtmaldives','Lagoon Oasis','inherit','closed','closed','','w-maldives-lagoon-oasis-tmtmaldives','','','2016-10-15 02:27:38','2016-10-14 20:42:38','',466,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/W-Maldives-Lagoon-Oasis-tmtMaldives.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(468,1,'2016-10-15 02:38:34','2016-10-14 20:53:34','Retreat back in the comforts of over water wow ocean escape. A private, secluded 2 bedroom villa, this villa offers direct access to the ocean. Spend your day swimming or snorkeling in the turquoise lagoon or relax and lounge in the comforts of sundeck. Swim in your private plunge pool or enjoy the ever changing aqua life from the glass flooring. Every moment will be well spent in this luxurious villa.\r\n\r\nThis villa features modern amenities including plasma TV, BOSE® sound system, 50 inch plasma TV, complimentary High, Speed Internet Access, wine fridge. This villa features a master bedroom with comfortable king size bed, outdoor bathroom featuring a standalone bathtub, rain forest shower, dining area, living area.','Wow Ocean Escape','','publish','closed','closed','','wow-ocean-escape','','','2016-10-15 02:38:34','2016-10-14 20:53:34','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/?post_type=room&#038;p=468',0,'room','',0),(470,1,'2016-10-15 02:38:23','2016-10-14 20:53:23','','w-maldives-ocean-escape-tmtmaldives','Wow Ocean Escape','inherit','closed','closed','','w-maldives-ocean-escape-tmtmaldives','','','2016-10-15 02:38:32','2016-10-14 20:53:32','',468,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/W-Maldives-Ocean-escape-tmtMaldives.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(471,1,'2016-10-15 02:45:38','2016-10-14 21:00:38','Extreme wow ocean escape haven is the ultimate cozy, plush, luxurious villas W retreat and spa offers. Dreams come true in this beautiful villa, perfectly set over the water in a perfect harmony with the nature. Wake up to the sounds of the invigorating waves in this rustic thatched roof villa. The villa has a vibrant ambience with extensive custom furnishing and amenities. \r\n\r\nThe master suite features a king size bed, en-suite bathroom with oversized bathtub and bliss spa bath amenities. Offering an unobstructed view of the lagoon, this villa features a 42 inch plasma TV, wardrobe for him and her, IDD telephone. The junior suite is a sea facing suite featuring twin beds, en-suite bathroom, 42 inch plasma TV, and wardrobe for him and her.\r\n\r\nEnjoy the airy living area featuring a 50 inch plasma TV and Bose hi-fi set, kitchen area and outdoor deck. Enjoy the ever changing marine life and spacious outdoor deck in the extreme wow ocean Haven.','Extreme Wow Ocean Haven','','publish','closed','closed','','extreme-wow-ocean-haven','','','2016-10-15 02:45:38','2016-10-14 21:00:38','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/?post_type=room&#038;p=471',0,'room','',0),(472,1,'2016-10-15 02:45:29','2016-10-14 21:00:29','','w-maldives-extreme-wow-ocean-haven-tmtmaldives','Extreme Wow Ocean Haven','inherit','closed','closed','','w-maldives-extreme-wow-ocean-haven-tmtmaldives','','','2016-10-15 02:45:36','2016-10-14 21:00:36','',471,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/W-Maldives-Extreme-Wow-Ocean-Haven-tmtMaldives.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(479,1,'2016-10-15 02:51:46','2016-10-14 21:06:46','<strong>Fifteen Below</strong>\r\nThe only underwater night club and bar, dance to the tunes of DJ at fifteen below. It’s a perfect place to get your dancing shoes out and party hard with friends.\r\n\r\n<strong>Sip Bar</strong>\r\nEnjoy the encapsulating view of the sunset while sipping tropical cocktails, mocktails, chilled beer, extensive wine