st amazing house reefs, Angasna Ihuru. Just 20 minutes sea plane transfer from the airport, located at island of ihuru in north male atoll Angasana ihuru is a tiny island famous for its house reefs with colorful and variety of coral and fishes. An eco- friendly resort, it offers Eco-conservation programs, alongside snorkeling, reef excursions. You can also indulge yourself in the holistic spa treatment offered by professional therapist and invigorate your body and soul.\r\nRooms at Angsana ihuru are spacious, equipped with all the modern amenities and offering an exquisite view of the dazzling white talc sand and blue Deep Ocean.','Angsana Ihuru Maldives','','publish','closed','closed','','angsana-ihuru-maldives','','','2016-10-31 22:45:06','2016-10-31 17:45:06','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/?post_type=resort&#038;p=511',0,'resort','',0),(512,1,'2016-10-15 05:47:10','2016-10-15 00:02:10','','angsana-ihuru','Angsana Ihuru Maldives','inherit','closed','closed','','angsana-ihuru','','','2016-10-15 05:47:22','2016-10-15 00:02:22','',511,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Angsana-Ihuru.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(514,1,'2016-10-15 06:00:48','2016-10-15 00:15:48','Set across the chalky white sand, beachfront villa offers king size bed with a warm living area, vibrant ambience and a verandah with swing and chairs to enjoy the mesmerizing beauty of the island. Enjoy the outdoor rainfall shower too.','Beachfront Villa','','publish','closed','closed','','beachfront-villa','','','2016-10-15 06:00:48','2016-10-15 00:15:48','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/?post_type=room&#038;p=514',0,'room','',0),(515,1,'2016-10-15 06:00:21','2016-10-15 00:15:21','','angsana-ihuru-beachfront-villa','Beachfront-villa','inherit','closed','closed','','angsana-ihuru-beachfront-villa','','','2016-10-15 06:00:33','2016-10-15 00:15:33','',514,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Angsana-Ihuru-Beachfront-villa.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5