ayments to be submitted after you request to confirm your booking & upon our confirmation. Payments can be made by Credit Card through our secure online system or you may also pay by Wire Transfers (Bank to Bank).\r\n\r\n<strong>When do i get my Booking Confirmation?</strong>\r\nWe try our best to provide you the confirmation right after you have submitted payment, however, due to working hours and time difference sometimes instant confirmation is not possible. Nonetheless, you receive confirmation for your booking within a 24 hours time.\r\n\r\n<strong>Can i check or Re-confirm a Booking with Resort?</strong>\r\nOnce you have received your Booking confirmation Number you may contact Resort to reconfirm if your bookings exists. However, there is truly no need to do so - we cannot get a Booking Number from resort unless its an active booking. Confirmation numbers are advised after booking is confirmed only.\r\n\r\n<strong>Can i amend a confirm Booking?</strong>\r\nYes, you can always amend you booking with no additional charge whatsoever. However, please note if your booking falls within Resort cancellation period, you will be charged penalties as per resort\'s cancellation policy. Also, Room Rates may vary with travel periods - Please always check with us before amending a booking.\r\n\r\n<strong>Can i Cancel after Confirming / Will i be refunded?</strong>\r\nIf your reservation is being cancelled prior to cancellation period, you will be refunded in full. If your cancellation request is within Cancellation period - penalties will be charged as per policy.\r\n\r\n<strong>What is Cancellation policy?</strong>\r\nCancellation policy is a time period given by Resort for those who cannot make the trip or wish not to after confirming their Bookings. As a penalty certain amount of total or the whole amount is charged (based on time of cancellation). Resort policies on cancellation always vary and is set according to the Seasons. Please always check with us on these policies before you confirm a booking.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','FAQs','','inherit','closed','closed','','94-revision-v1','','','2016-10-18 02:20:09','2016-10-17 20:35:09','',94,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/94-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(569,1,'2016-10-18 02:40:40','2016-10-17 20:55:40','','Your Journey in Luxury and Beyond','','inherit','closed','closed','','168-revision-v1','','','2016-10-18 02:40:40','2016-10-17 20:55:40','',168,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/168-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(577,1,'2016-10-19 02:23:21','2016-10-18 20:38:21','Take me to Maldives Pvt. Ltd. more commonly referred as tmtMaldives is a Local travel operator based in Maldives. Company is registered and licensed by the Ministry of Tourism Arts and Culture for the sales and culture for the sales and endorsement of Maldives Island Resorts.\r\n\r\nOur main goal is to offer our clients all data and direction they require, with a specific end goal to help them settle for the best choice about which Maldivian Resort to visit, at the most moderate costs. At present we have more than 80 Island Resorts listed for visitors to choose from. Sometimes, finding an ideal resort within your requirement can be confusing, while you decide on a resort our team makes sure you have all information you may require to confirm a resort for your holiday.\r\n\r\nOur team has time to time visited all these islands which allows us to advise you with key facts and information about resort you choose for your stay. We are impassioned about creating the best holidays experience for you by going an extra mile to make sure you get exactly what you want, the way you want it.\r\n\r\n','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','88-revision-v1','','','2016-10-19 02:23:21','2016-10-18 20:38:21','',88,'http://tmtmaldives.com/beta/88-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(578,1,'2016-10-19 02:27:29','2016-10-18 20:42:29','','FLEXIBLE','','inherit','closed','closed','','203-revision-v1','','