.com/tmtmal/?post_type=room&#038;p=677',0,'room','',0),(678,1,'2016-10-30 10:14:19','2016-10-30 05:14:19','Overlooking the breathtaking azure lagoons, ocean lagoon houses is a well-designed and well equipped house offering guest complete relaxation. This contemporary villa offers outdoor deck featuring a private plunge pool, well-furnished for sunbathing, dining and relaxing. Inside the villa features air-conditioner, 42 inch satellite TV, a separate indoor living room area with sofa and work desk, a Minibar, in and outdoor showers and a bathroom with bath tub.','Ocean Lagoon House','','publish','closed','closed','','ocean-lagoon-house','','','2016-10-30 10:24:43','2016-10-30 05:24:43','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=room&#038;p=678',0,'room','',0),(679,1,'2016-10-30 10:14:05','2016-10-30 05:14:05','','amilla-fushi-ocean-lagoon-house','Ocean Lagoon House','inherit','closed','closed','','amilla-fushi-ocean-lagoon-house','','','2016-10-30 10:14:16','2016-10-30 05:14:16','',678,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Amilla-fushi-Ocean-lagoon-house.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(680,1,'2016-10-30 10:24:32','2016-10-30 05:24:32','Nestled in the lush vegetation of the island, beach house is the ideal choice for travelers who want to be close to nature. The beach house features a private courtyard featuring swimming pool, dining area, hammocks. Designed for beach lovers this contemporary villa features master bedroom with en-suite bathroom with in- and outdoor showers and a bath tub, 42 inch flat-screen TV and satellite channels, an indoor living room area with sofa and work desk, a minibar.','Beach House','','publish','closed','closed','','beach-house','','','2016-10-30 10:24:32','2016-10-30 05:24:32','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=room&#038;p=680',0,'room','',0),(681,1,'2016-10-30 10:23:42','2016-10-30 05:23:42','','amilla-fushi-beach-house','Beach House','inherit','closed','closed','','amilla-fushi-beach-house','',