nd pasta with your loved ones.\r\n\r\n<strong>Aqua:</strong>\r\nFor all those honeymooners this is the place to eat. Located on the poolside it offers lunch with live music. The diners can enjoy the perfect view of the sunset , enjoying their meal.\r\n\r\n<strong>Dining by design: </strong>\r\nThis restaurant designs your perfect romantic candlelit dinner with Maldivian foods being served.\r\n\r\n<strong>Baan Hura: </strong>\r\nIt’s Thai in Maldives. Maybe one of the finest Thai restaurant in Maldives guests can enjoy coconut curries, hot and spicy dishes from Thai. The restaurant ambience, food makes you feel you’re in Thailand.\r\n\r\n<strong>73 degrees:</strong>\r\nOffers buffet-style sumptuous breakfast and dinner to its guests\r\n\r\n<strong>Origami:</strong> \r\nThis is chic Japanese restaurant serving with a choice of Japanese foods ranging from sushi to sashimi to slow charcoal grilled robatayaki skewers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Dhoni:</strong>\r\nLocated just near the infinity pool. Guests can swim and enjoy their drinks catching the glimpse of the beautiful sunset.','Restaurants & Bars','','publish','closed','closed','','restaurants-bars-2','','','2016-10-30 12:52:57','2016-10-30 07:52:57','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=dining&#038;p=709',0,'dining','',0),(710,1,'2016-10-31 04:41:59','2016-10-30 23:41:59','If your idea of an ideal holiday is being marooned in the middle of Indian Ocean, surrounded by uninhabited island, palm dotted sands, pristine azure ocean, bright sunlight, secluded villas and iconic dining avenues than Anantara Kivavah Maldives is the perfect choice for you.\r\n\r\nJust 35-minute seaplane flight from Male International Airport, you reach this magical luxury resort, Anatara Kihavah Maldives. The resort offers 79 secluded villas on plam dotted sands  and over water. Relish scenic beauties from the deck of your private villa. An intimate experience.\r\n\r\nPositioned in UNESCO World Biosphere Reserve, you can explore worlds most jeweled reefs here at Anantara Kihavah. Snorkel deep under to home of turtles, eels, and corals and rediscover yourself. Now if you don’t want to go underwater, there are some many activities outside water. Enjoy one of a kind underwater restaurant, Sea. Play tennis, hit gym, swim in the infinity pool or simply unwind at Anatara Spa.\r\n\r\nDiscover your own paradise.\r\n','Anantara Kihavah Maldives Villas','','publish','closed','closed','','anantara-kihavah-maldives-villas','','','2016-11-01 19:38:46','2016-11-01 14:38:46','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=resort&#038;p=710',0,'resort','',0),(711,1,'2016-10-31 04:45:55','2016-10-30 23:45:55','Capture the stunning view of sunrise from the comforts of your bed. This 258 square meter villa surrounded by lush vegetation is set just few meters away from the ocean. Inspired by Maldivian architecture, the villa has a thatched roof, large windows letting the natural sunlight in. An ideal place to stay for couples, the villa features a romantic sunken bathtub just for two. Step outside the villa, enjoy few lapses in swimming pool, or sit over the deck and enjoy the skies tapestry.','Beach Pool Villa','','publish','closed','closed','','beach-pool-villa','','','2016-10-31 04:45:55','2016-10-30 23:45:55','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=room&#038;p=711',0,'room','',0),(712,1,'2016-10-31 04:54:36','2016-10-30 23:54:36','With all the facilities of beach pool villa, this villa is positioned to capture the romantic Maldivian sunsets across Baa Atoll. This 258 square meter villa is spacious, elegant, well-equipped, well-furnished and provides complete seclusion and privacy. \r\n\r\nHardwood furnished villa, the villa features a bedroom with king size bed with Egyptian cotton and range of pillow. Expansive bathroom with outdoor shower.','Sunset Beach Pool Villa','','publish','closed','closed','','sunset-beach-pool-villa','','','2016-10-31 04:54:36','2016-10-30 23:54:36','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?p