rong>In-villa dining</strong>\r\nLazy to go out for dining, the resort offers international cuisines in the comfort and privacy of your villas.\r\n\r\n','Restaurants & Bars','','publish','closed','closed','','restaurants-bars-13','','','2016-11-01 17:25:52','2016-11-01 12:25:52','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=dining&#038;p=871',0,'dining','',0),(874,1,'2016-11-02 06:34:33','2016-11-02 01:34:33','Indulge into a complete serene tropical holiday in Maldives at Centara Res Fushi Resort and Spa. An adult only resort (12 years and above) located at the unspoiled island of North male atoll is only 20 minutes speedboat ride from Ibrahim Nassir International airport. \r\n\r\nOn land or above the water wherever you want to stay, each villa is well designed and well furnished with an overlooking view of the magical ocean.  Inspired by the traditional Maldivian culture, the villas have thatched roof, long windows letting the cool breeze awaken your senses.\r\n\r\nEnjoy the aromatic signature dishes, invigorating drinks at different dining avenues set across the island. \r\n\r\nIn the endless white sandy beaches wouldn’t it be nice to play some beach games. Dive, snorkel into the crystal clear ocean and discover the enchanting underwater world.  And after all the play retreat back to the spa and heal your body and mind with the sublime massages and therapy. \r\n\r\nA resort designed for couples and honeymooners, scorch the romance at this intimate haven. \r\n','Centara Ras Fushi Resort & Spa','','publish','closed','closed','','centara-ras-fushi-resort-spa','','','2016-11-06 13:18:53','2016-11-06 08:18:53','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=resort&#038;p=874',0,'resort','',0),(877,1,'2016-11-02 06:43:49','2016-11-02 01:43:49','','Centara Ras Fushi Resort &amp; Spa Maldives','Centara Ras Fushi Resort &amp; Spa Maldives','inherit','closed','closed','','centara-ras-fushi-resort-spa-maldives','','','2016-11-02 06:43:49','2016-11-02 01:43:49','',874,'http:/