atch the world go by in the casual setting of our lobby bar. Enjoy a choice of hot and cold refreshments, exotic juices and cocktails throughout the day and evenings.\r\n\r\n<strong>In-villa dining</strong>\r\nIn-Villa dining option available for guests round o\' clock.','Restaurants & Bars','','publish','closed','closed','','restaurants-bars-14','','','2016-11-02 07:37:42','2016-11-02 02:37:42','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=dining&#038;p=888',0,'dining','',0),(889,1,'2016-11-02 07:59:58','2016-11-02 02:59:58','Your unforgettable tropical holiday of sun kissed lagoon, palm fringed beaches and panoramic blue ocean awaits you at the sunny resort, Cheval Blanc. Located in preserved and unspoiled oasis of Noonu Atoll, you can reach this resort through a picturesque 40 minute seaplane ride from capital, Male.\r\n One of the most stylish resort in Maldives, the resort has been the choice for celebrities, fashion monger and even the duke and duchess of Cambridge.\r\n\r\nTucked away from all the hustle and bustle of mundane life, enjoy peace and seclusion in the villas offered by the resort. Home away from home, the villas are comfortable with all the  modern amenities and necessities needed.\r\n\r\nHome to stunning samples of multicolored fish, rays and sea turtles, coral reefs one can enjoy their time diving, snorkeling and exploring the aquatic life. For the ones who want to relax, one can take pamper massages in Cheval Blanc spa or savor mouthwatering cuisines under the moonlit or just soak in the sun at endless pure white sand beaches .\r\n','Cheval Blanc Randheli','','publish','closed','closed','','cheval-blanc-randheli','','','2016-11-02 07:59:58','2016-11-02 02:59:58','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=resort&#038;p=889',0,'resort','',0),(890,1,'2016-11-02 07:59:28','2016-11-02 02:59:28','','cheval-balnc-randheli','Cheval Balnc Randheli','inherit','closed','closed','','cheval-balnc-randheli','','','2016-11-02 07:59:36','2016-11-02 02:59: