d Thai specialities with a teppanyaki table for a real Asian combination food encounter and creative presentation.\r\n\r\n<strong>Ocean Grill </strong>Visit the beachfront Ocean Grill and devour seafood and heavenly meat, freshly prepared on the live grill and seasoned with natural herbs, straight from the island garden. Enjoy the evening island breeze penetrated with delectable scents and fresh flavors for an awesome dining background under the stars.\r\n\r\n<strong>Kakuni</strong> Begin your day on the island with a definitive breakfast experience with Kakuni, serving an awesome breakfast buffet with gourmet choices from over the globe. While dinner will take you on a culinary experience from round the globe and Maldivian themed night selections and in addition International a la carte on other evenings.\r\n\r\n<strong>The Cellar </strong>Encounter haute cooking and explore the award winning \'wine cave\' offering a broad choice of fine wines from prestigious vineyards around the globe. The Cellar is situated more than two meters beneath ocean level and is a romantic, candlelit, underground haven.\r\n\r\n<strong>Andiamo Bistro and Pool</strong> For lunch or dinner be transported to the shores of the Mediterranean and enjoy a kaleidoscope of colors, scents and flavors with a home-made pizza, pasta and plates of salads, settled inside a rich desert garden around the resort pool - bellissimo!\r\n\r\n<strong>Infinity Bar &amp; Pool </strong>With consistent views to the horizon, Infinity Pool Bar is the ideal spot to enjoy a crisp serving of salads, scrumptious sandwich or light snack, for the duration of the day.\r\n\r\n<strong>Horizon Lounge</strong> No visit to JA Manafaru would be finished without setting aside the opportunity to encounter a delighted dusk at Horizon Lounge. Relaxation will come easily, as you take in the energetic changing horizon reflected over the perfect waters with one of the signature cocktail in hand.','Restaurants & Bars','','publish','closed','closed','','restaurants-bars-36','','','2016-11-27 02:30:58','2016-11-26 21:30:58','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=dining&#038;p=1329',0,'dining','',0),(1330,1,'2016-11-27 13:37:08','2016-11-27 08:37:08','Enjoy the sun, sand, beaches and scrumptious exotic drinks at Jumeriah Vittaveli, where dreams never ends. Located at south male atoll in the amazing Boolifushi Island, Jumeriah Vittaveli is just a 20-minute ride from male international airport. From male international airport you will transferred to a luxurious motorized catamaran through which you reach this exotic resort. Jumeirah Vittaveli offers an impeccable experience for all the honeymooners and families on their exotic holiday. Enjoy the authentic Maldivian hospitality with plush villas and luxury services.\r\n\r\nThe resort offers 89 villas and suites located across the beach and over the ocean, offers panoramic view of the ocean, direct access to the beach or lagoon and a private swimming pool. The villas are spacious, well-equipped and ideal for both families on exotic holiday and honeymooners on romantic getaway.\r\n\r\nJumeirah Vittaveli offers an unmatched luxury and wellness facilities including a 5 star PADI dive center, Talise Spa and Talise Fitness,  Kuda Koli Kid’s club for the kids. Located in south male atoll which is home to the healthiest and colorful house reefs, guest can go on an underwater exploration. Enjoy the aroma and savor exquisite delight at one of the four restaurants and bar.','Jumeirah Vittaveli Maldives','','publish','closed','closed','','jumeirah-vittaveli-maldives','','','2016-11-28 20:22:08','2016-11-28 15:22:08','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=resort&#038;p=1330',0,'resort','',0),(1331,1,'2016-11-27 13:36:56','2016-11-27 08:36:56','','jumeirah-vittaveli-maldives','Jumeirah Vittaveli Maldives','inherit','closed','closed','','jumeirah-vittaveli-maldives','','','2016-11-27 13:37:04','2016-11-27 08:37:04','',1330,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtma