/strong>This fine dining French restaurant in the Maldives opens its entryways each night to entice your palate in a rich yet warm setting. Including contemporary cuisine enlivened by the culinary locales of France, enjoy the freshest ingredients at Fenesse prepared by devoted group of professional chefs.\r\n\r\n<strong>MU BEACH BAR &amp; GRILL</strong> The ideal setting for both private candle light dinners on the beach and also family style dining, MU Beach Bar and Grill serves the absolute best meats in the Maldives in various marble scores and the freshest seafood including lobster, prawns and fish cooked to flawlessly on grill.\r\n\r\n<strong>BAR-EE</strong> Perched over the water, come and enjoy lazy afternoon soaking up to the view of idyllic sunset at Bar-ee. It offers 360 degree bar\'s menu of signature cocktails, fine wine, and tropical juices and makes it a perfect place for refreshing or relaxing.\r\n\r\n<strong>SAMSARA </strong>serves enticing sumptuous Asian and international cuisines in a la carte and buffet style all day long. Savor the freshest sashimi, seafood curry or pork chops in this eclectic culinary restaurant.\r\n\r\n<strong>PRIVATE DINING </strong>Your imagination of a private dinner at the most romantic location come true at Jumeriah Vittaveli. The resort arranges private dining with personal chefs cooking culinary masterpiece just for two. Lunch beside the infinity pool or dine under the stars or in a uninhabited island choice is yours.','Restaurants & Bars','','publish','closed','closed','','restaurants-bars-37','','','2016-11-27 15:26:47','2016-11-27 10:26:47','',0,'http://tmtmaldives.com/tmtmal/?post_type=dining&#038;p=1347',0,'dining','',0),(1348,1,'2016-11-27 15:42:30','2016-11-27 10:42:30','<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Book by </strong>31st March 2017 &amp; receive 30% off from room rates along with complimentary half board.\r\n<strong>For Stay in-between </strong>1st May 2017 – 30th September 2017.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>B